snippet.title: This Is the President - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
You’re the newly elected President and you need to change the Constitution to escape justice. How do you do that?

Well that’s fairly obvious, isn’t it? Watch this Gameplay Trailer for This Is the President and find out!

Just don’t get impeached before doing that -- and you’re golden.
